title: "LLM Atlas: an interactive transformer visualization"
abstract: "An interactive, in-browser visualization of how a transformer language model works, covering tokenization, embeddings, multi-head attention, per-layer transforms, weight quantization, and sampling, rendered live on a custom Canvas 2D engine with no dependencies."
